Annotations
 
This is the XML Schema Tables module for XHTML
$Id$

xhtml-copyright-1.xsd

Tables
      
     * table, caption, thead, tfoot, tbody, colgroup, col, tr, th, td
      
    This module declares element types and attributes used to provide
    table markup similar to HTML 4.0, including features that enable
    better accessibility for non-visual user agents.

http://www.w3.org/TR/2001/REC-xhtml-modularization-20010410/abstract_modules.html#s_tablemodule
